WEBVTT

00:05:29.867 --> 00:05:31.442
in the same way, right?

00:05:32.740 --> 00:05:34.500
Some are more serious than others --

00:05:34.524 --> 00:05:35.530
(Laughter)

00:05:35.554 --> 00:05:37.257
but still, the toothbrush is there.

00:05:37.281 --> 00:05:39.934
And then, coming down to this poorer end,

00:05:39.958 --> 00:05:42.634
then we will see people
start using sticks,

00:05:43.768 --> 00:05:47.482
and they will sometimes use their finger
to brush their teeth.

00:05:48.016 --> 00:05:50.489
So this particular woman in Malawi,

00:05:50.513 --> 00:05:52.105
when she brushes her teeth,

00:05:52.129 --> 00:05:54.232
she scrapes some mud off from her wall

00:05:54.256 --> 00:05:57.160
and she mixes it with water,
and then she's brushing.

00:05:57.184 --> 00:05:59.954
Therefore, in the Dollar Street material,

00:05:59.978 --> 00:06:02.088
we have tagged this image